<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>SoulBorn</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nanum+Gothic" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

    <div class="zebra text-center">
        <h1>Do You Agree With This Timeline</h1>
        <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vT_4jf02wsU" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        <h2>I agree with this timeline, VaatiVidya made some good points. The fact that Bloodborne had content talking about a Demon Souls god is good proof that the creator want to have the souls worlds connected. It would make a lot of sense for them to do that</h2>
        <div class="">
          <h3>Your Thoughs</h3>
          <ul class="messages">
          <% for(var i=0; i<messages.length; i++) {%>
            <li class="message">
              <span><%= messages[i].name %></span>
              <span><%= messages[i].msg %></span>
              <span><%= messages[i].thumbUp %></span>
              <span><i class="fa fa-thumbs-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
              <span><%= messages[i].thumbDown %></span>
              <span><i class="fa fa-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
              <span><i class="fas fa-trash-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            </li>
          <% } %>
          </ul>

        <form action="/messages" method="POST">
          <input type="text" name="name" value="" placeholder="Name">
          <input type="text" name="msg" value="" placeholder="Thoughs">
          <button type="submit" name="button">Submit</button>
        </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-default"><span class="fa fa-user"></span>Creator Log In</a>
</div>
<script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
